# CPRS

Legacy ExtJS / Spring Roo admin app remains under `src/`.

## New Review Platform

Modern stack:

- Root `pom.xml` — Spring Boot 4 executable **JAR** (Java 25 + Drools 10); legacy Roo/WAR deps removed
- `apps/review-platform/backend/src` — API sources
- `apps/review-platform/frontend` — Angular UI

```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```

Start with:

- `docs/plans/00-overview.md`
- `docs/plans/05-cursor-skills-guide.md`
- `apps/review-platform/README.md`
